column16: What was the total amount of arrears?
column17: Over how many months did the arrears accumulate?

column19: Did the decision mention a history of arrears by the tenant separate from the arrears in the current claim (more than one period of arrears, recurrently coming in and out of arrears, arrears with previous landlord, etc.)?
